<p>-<a href="http://www.girlgeniusonline.com/comic.php?date=20090323" rel="nofollow">Gilgamesh Wulfenbach</a></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1v2h"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1v2h" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1v2h')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1v2h" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1v2h')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1v2h" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/20y/rationality_quotes_april_2010/1v2h?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1v2h" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1v2h')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1v2h class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1v2h" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1uxk" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1uxk" class="parent"><a name="1uxk" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1uxk" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1uxk" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1uxk" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Lightwave/">Lightwave</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 05:57:53PM</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uxk'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1uxk')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1uxk" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1uxk" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Lightwave/">Lightwave</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 05:57:53PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1uxk'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uxk'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1uxk')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1uxk" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
