<p>Sir Arthur Conan Doyle, <em>The Sign of Four, A Scandal in Bohemia</em></p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1uxk"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1uxk" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uxk')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1uxk" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uxk')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1uxk" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/20y/rationality_quotes_april_2010/1uxk?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1uxk" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1uxk')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1uxk class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1uxk" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1uwd" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1uwd" class="parent"><a name="1uwd" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1uwd" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1uwd" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1uwd" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/NancyLebovitz/">NancyLebovitz</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 11:25:48AM</span><span class="votes " >3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uwd'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1uwd')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1uwd" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1uwd" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/NancyLebovitz/">NancyLebovitz</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 11:25:48AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1uwd'>3 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uwd'] = ['2 points', '3 points', '4 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1uwd')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1uwd" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>We must be careful who we let define what is sustainable.</p>

<p>Jason Stoddard in <a href="http://www.amazon.com/Shine-Anthology-Optomistic-Jetse-Vries/dp/1906735670/ref=sr_1_1?ie=UTF8&amp;s=books&amp;qid=1259057186&amp;sr=1-1" rel="nofollow">Shine</a>, an anthology of near-future optimistic science fiction.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1uwd"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1uwd" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uwd')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1uwd" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uwd')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1uwd" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/20y/rationality_quotes_april_2010/1uwd?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1uwd" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1uwd')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1uwd class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1uwd" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1uss" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1uss" class="parent"><a name="1uss" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1uss" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1uss" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1uss" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Vladimir_Golovin/">Vladimir_Golovin</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">06 April 2010 10:35:21AM</span><span class="votes " >4 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uss'] = ['3 points', '4 points', '5 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1uss')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1uss" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1uss" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Vladimir_Golovin/">Vladimir_Golovin</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">