eta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1uoe" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/MichaelGR/">MichaelGR</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">05 April 2010 06:36:34AM</span><span class="votes " >8 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uoe'] = ['7 points', '8 points', '9 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1uoe')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1uoe" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1uoe" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/MichaelGR/">MichaelGR</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">05 April 2010 06:36:34AM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1uoe'>8 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uoe'] = ['7 points', '8 points', '9 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1uoe')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1uoe" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
