d='score_t1_1uia'>6 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uia'] = ['5 points', '6 points', '7 points' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1uia')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1uia" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
