<p>I had never previously considered the possibility of James Callaghan uploading into an internet-connected paperclip maximizer, but I guess there's a first time for everything.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1v0g"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1v0g" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1v0g')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1v0g" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1v0g')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1v0g" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/20y/rationality_quotes_april_2010/1v0g?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_1v0g" href="#1uyo" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1v0g" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1v0g')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1v0g class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1v0g" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1uz0" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1uz0" class="parent"><a name="1uz0" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1uz0" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1uz0" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1uz0" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Matt_Simpson/">Matt_Simpson</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 08:47:58PM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uz0'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1uz0')">[+] (1 child)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1uz0" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1uz0" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Matt_Simpson/">Matt_Simpson</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 08