<p>The great paperclip crash of 07</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1uz0"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1uz0" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uz0')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1uz0" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uz0')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1uz0" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/20y/rationality_quotes_april_2010/1uz0?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_1uz0" href="#1uyo" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1uz0" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1uz0')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1uz0 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1uz0" class="child" ><div id="siteTable_t1_1uz0" class="sitetable"><div id="ajaxHook_t1_1uz0" class="ajaxhook"></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1uz8" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1uz8" class="parent"><a name="1uz8" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1uz8" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1uz8" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1uz8" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Jack/">Jack</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 09:12:39PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uz8'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1uz8')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1uz8" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1uz8" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Jack/">Jack</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 09:12:39PM<em>*</em>&nbsp;</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1uz8'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uz8'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1uz8')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1uz8" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><blockquote>
  <p>The great paperclip crash of 07</p>
</blockquote>

<p>This happened much earlier than 2007. The advent of electronic databases and office networks surely lead to rough times in the paperclip industry. Some analysts say that if we had paid more attention to the lesson of the 98' Paperclip Crisis we could have avoided all the problems we have today.</p></div></div><div style="display: none;" id="edit_body_t1_1uz8"></div><div class="comment-links"><ul class="clear"><li class="first"><a id="up_t1_1uz8" class="up" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uz8')" >Vote up</a></li><li><a id="down_t1_1uz8" class="down" onclick="showcover(true, 'vote_t1_1uz8')" >Vote down</a></li><li><a id="permalink_t1_1uz8" href="http://lesswrong.com/lw/20y/rationality_quotes_april_2010/1uz8?c=1" class=" " target="_parent" >Permalink</a></li><li><a id="parent_t1_1uz8" href="#1uz0" class="bylink">Parent</a></li><li><a id="reply_a_t1_1uz8" class="" href="javascript:reply('t1_1uz8')">Reply</a></li></ul><span id=status_t1_1uz8 class="error" style="display: none;"></span></div></div></div><div id="child_t1_1uz8" class="child" ></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div></div><div class="clearleft"><!--IE6sux--></div><div id="thingrow_t1_1uyr" class="comment" ><div id="pre_t1_1uyr" class="parent"><a name="1uyr" ></a></div><div id="entry_t1_1uyr" class="entry"><div id="collapsed_t1_1uyr" class="comment-meta collapsed clear " style='display:none'><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author gray"><a id="author_t1_1uyr" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Thomas/">Thomas</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 08:12:22PM</span><span class="votes " >0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uyr'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return showcomment('t1_1uyr')">[+] (0 children)</a></div><div id="display_t1_1uyr" class="" ><div class="comment-meta clear"><span class="comment-author"><strong><span class="author"><a id="author_t1_1uyr" href="http://lesswrong.com/user/Thomas/">Thomas</a></span></strong></span><span class="comment-date">07 April 2010 08:12:22PM</span><span class="votes " id='score_t1_1uyr'>0 points</span><script type="text/javascript">vl['t1_1uyr'] = ['-1 points', '0 points', '1 point' ];</script>&#32;<a href="#" class="expand" onclick="return hidecomment('t1_1uyr')">[-]</a></div><div id="body_t1_1uyr" class="comment-content"><div class="md"><p>If that's a real fact, that a crisis is unpredictable (what might be, I don't know), than the knowledge of this fact is more valuable than an accidental prediction of one crises.</p>

